1
00:00:18,920 --> 00:00:20,000
Little lady,

2
00:00:20,320 --> 00:00:21,680
let me give you some fun

3
00:00:22,480 --> 00:00:24,680
on your wedding night.

4
00:00:31,760 --> 00:00:34,280
Is that all you can do to kill me?

5
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:49,840
You're crazy!

6
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:51,680
Madwoman!

7
00:01:14,840 --> 00:01:15,480
Mother!

8
00:01:16,040 --> 00:01:16,600
Mother!

9
00:01:18,360 --> 00:01:19,160
Mother!

10
00:01:25,200 --> 00:01:27,200
Father!

11
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:34,600
Take the seal and keep it safe.

12
